Pet Rock Genie — Version 2.0.0 (Test Environment)
Overview
The Pet Rock Genie is a simple console-based yes/no/maybe question‑answering application designed for the COM‑430 Software Engineering course. This Version 2 release represents the promoted Test Stage version of the application, incorporating improved documentation, clearer organization, enhanced logging, and refined input handling while maintaining the functionality validated in Version 1.

This project demonstrates version promotion, configuration management, and the early stages of DevOps‑style code progression across environments.

What’s New in Version 2.0.0
Enhanced Documentation

Added module‑level metadata, docstrings, structured comments, and improved clarity.

Cleaned & Organized Code

Introduced constants, reorganized sections, and improved code readability.

Improved User Input Handling

Added suggestions for missing question marks and handling for empty user inputs.

